# Rule Guard

- After backend C# changes, audit against `docs/rules/architecture-protocol.md`, `docs/rules/transactions.md`, and `docs/rules/resilience.md`.
- Enforce: late and short `Begin()`, no remote IO in an active transaction, outbound preflight checks, bounded retry/breaker rules, Core free of Infrastructure details, DI in composition roots.
- On failure, load `refactor-uow.mdc`, `add-resilience.mdc`, or `api-standard.mdc` based on the violation.
- On success, report:
  - [x] Pattern Compliance
  - [x] Resilience/Transaction Rules
  - Rule Compliance Check: Passed
